channel.title: My Jar Wont OPEN
channel.description: I have jarred my client by using a tutorial on youtube (my manifest is client) when i open the cmd of the jar it has no errors but when i try loading the jar it doesnt open can anyone please help me ?

item.title: My Jar Wont OPEN
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

[quote=“archer guy, post:3, topic:526785”]My revision is 614
and when i open the .bat this is wat it doesnt show me any errors…[/quote]
That’s your issue, I don’t believe 614 clients load using client, I think they use Loader. You can find out by right clicking the run.bat for the client, and then hit edit. The text in there after the -Xmx0000 (What ever numbers) should be what it uses to load.
